{"tid":945434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【廉航合併】樂桃航空明年5月起整合香草航線網絡","createTime":"2018-12-18T01:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T02:24:44.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"31d0d30c23732c67159c9283ec5e704975e1c484","tid":945434,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:30:52.000Z","msg":"同屬全日空（ANA）旗下的廉航樂桃航空（Peach）和香草航空（Vanilla Air）將於明年合併，後者航線網絡明年5月起逐步整合到樂桃旗下，並於10月底結束營運。<br />\n<br />\n整合預定於5月6日展開，屆時香草會結束每日往返大阪關西機場和奄美大島的航線，而往來東京成田和香港、以及沖繩那霸和石垣的航線則於同月31日結束。<br />\n<br />\n而在正式整合前，香草3月30日會結束往返東京成田和北海道的航線。<br />\n<br />\n不過，樂桃將於6月28日新推出往返沖繩和香港的航線，並在10月27日起增加東京成田和大阪前往石垣的航機班次。<br />\n<br />\n撰文 : 陳啟賢<br />\n<a href=\"https://wealth.hket.com/article/2232424/%E3%80%90%E5%BB%89%E8%88%AA%E5%90%88%E4%BD%B5%E3%80%91%E6%A8%82%E6%A1%83%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B45%E6%9C%88%E8%B5%B7%E6%95%B4%E5%90%88%E9%A6%99%E8%8D%89%E8%88%AA%E7%B7%9A%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%C2%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwealth.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2232424%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25BB%2589%25E8%2588%25AA%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%25B5%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25A8%2582%25E6%25A1%2583%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B45%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%2595%25B4%25E5%2590%2588%25E9%25A6%2599%25E8%258D%2589%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25B7%259A%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B5%25A1%25C2%25A0&d=LTtkzNEE4HXdLZFdqzpendibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b57abae9\" target=\"_blank\">https://wealth.hket.com/article/2232424/%E3%80%90%E5%BB%89%E8%88%AA%E5%90%88%E4%BD%B5%E3%80%91%E6%A8%82%E6%A1%83%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B45%E6%9C%88%E8%B5%B7%E6%95%B4%E5%90%88%E9%A6%99%E8%8D%89%E8%88%AA%E7%B7%9A%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%C2%A0</a>"},{"pid":"61df07b6fc5d12650ec6fa321186aaa09fec3551","tid":945434,"uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:36:24.000Z","msg":"打柒支那快運"},{"pid":"3ccf0cc3af425b05aef482afcb1a05895f2ee7d6","tid":945434,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci